Package jdkc_exchange

Class Member

  • java.lang.Object
    • jdkc_exchange.Member
  • public class Member
extends java.lang.Object
    A class which implements the concept of a Member individual. The Member class allows the user to identify as an individual in the system. Members are unique on email and screen name. Members also contain additional information such as their first and last names, the date which they were created, and their membership list. The Member alone cannot participate in the system without memberships. It is not until a Member joins a Group that they can make posts.
    See Also:
    Membership
